flowchart TD
    A([comparison view called]) --> B[Query FlowExecution rows by ids]
    B --> C{Any executions\nfound?}
    C -- No --> D([render empty state])
    C -- Yes --> E[Define INPUT_KEYS =\nincome, age, credit_score,\nemployment_years]
    E --> F[For each input key:\ncollect values across all executions]
    F --> G{All values\nfor key identical?}
    G -- Yes --> H[Mark key as SAME]
    G -- No --> I[Mark key as DIFFERS]
    H & I --> J["Build comparison_data list per execution:\n inputs = {k: params[k] for k in INPUT_KEYS}\nresult = {score, classification, confidence}\nfrom parameters\n duration from timestamps"]
    J --> K[Pass differing_fields set to template]
    K --> L([render comparison.html])

    L --> M{User clicks\nExport CSV?}
    M -- No --> N([done])
    M -- Yes --> O[GET /flows/comparison/export/?ids=...]
    O --> P[Re-query executions for user]
    P --> Q[Build CSV rows:\nheader: field + exec short-ids\nrows: each INPUT_KEY value\nrows: score, classification,\nconfidence]
    Q --> R([StreamingHttpResponse text/csv\nattachment download])
